Get drugs known to target a given EnsemblId product

ot_knowndrugs.Rd

Get drugs known to target a given EnsemblId product

Usage

ot_knowndrugs(ensgIds, size = 1000)

Arguments

ensgIds

Character vector of EnsemblIDs

size

Maximum number of rows to return per EnsemblID queried

Value

A tibble

Examples


ot_knowndrugs("ENSG00000157764")
